    <etym xml:lang="ru">Образовано от <ref type="xr" target="#entry_fæsm"/> ‘шерсть’ с помощью
        суффикса %i-yn%i (← <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>-aina</w></mentioned>). Ср.
            <mentioned xml:lang="fa"
            ><lang/><w>pašmīn</w><gloss><q>шерстяной</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"
                ><w>pašmīna</w><gloss><q>шерстяной</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>шерстяная ткань или одежда</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned
            xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>pemminaa</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (из
                %i*pašmīna%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (from
                    %i*pašmīna%i)</note><gloss><q>шерстяной</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref
                target="#ref_Konow._SSt."/><biblScope>169</biblScope></bibl>). Дигорская форма
        %ifæsbun%i, по-видимому, вторичная, возникшая под влиянием <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_tæbyn"/> | %i*tæbun%i ‘шерстяной’?</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Derived from <ref type="xr" target="#entry_fæsm"/> ‘wool’ with the suffix
        %i-yn%i (← <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>-aina</w></mentioned>). Cf. <mentioned
            xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>pašmīn</w><gloss><q>woollen</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="fa"><w>pašmīna</w><gloss><q>woollen</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="fa"><w/><gloss><q>woollen cloth or clothes</q></gloss></mentioned>, ,
            <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>pemminaa</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (из
                %i*pašmīna%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (from
                    %i*pašmīna%i)</note><gloss><q>woollen</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref
                target="#ref_Konow._SSt."/><biblScope>169</biblScope></bibl>). Apparently the Digor
        form %ifæsbun%i is secondary, which appered under the influence of <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_tæbyn"/> | %i*tæbun%i ‘woollen’?</etym>
